== 發行 ==
=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度僅16%，基於19條評論，平均分為4/10<ref name="rottentomatoes">{{cite web | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stolen_2012/ | title = Stolen | work = [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] | publisher = {{link-en|Flixster|Flixster}} | accessdate = December 27, 2014 | archive-date = 2019-03-31 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190331081058/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/stolen_2012 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到43分，[[IMDB|IMDB]]上得5.5分，收穫普遍差評。
=== 票房 ===
